{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef216cabae","title":"对刘少奇在全国组织工作会议上的报告稿的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"970e1ad8ae","index":0,"year":1951,"month":3,"day":30,"articleId":"ef216cabae"}],"tags":[{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"1833a84cd1","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ef216cabae","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘少奇报告稿第三部分“关于发展新党员的问题”中原来的一段话是：“党所领导的人民群众的团体，例如：新民主主义青年团、工会、农民协会、合作社、妇女联合会、文化工作者的团体等，都是党联系人民群众的纽带，也是党向人民群众进行共产主义教育的场所。凡有这些团体组织的地方，那里的工人、农民、青年、妇女或其他劳动人民入党，必须是这些团体的团员或会员，不能或不愿加入这些团体的人，也就是说，人民中的不良分子或落后分子，一般的不应该接收他们入党。毛泽东审阅时，删去了其中的“也就是说，人民中的不良分子或落后分子”。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e92a2f3e9c","type":"title","text":"对刘少奇在全国组织工作会议上的报告稿的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ef216cabae"},{"id":"1833a84cd1","type":"paragraph","text":"看过，同意。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ef216cabae"},{"id":"fc22e74b58","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ef216cabae"},{"id":"87af0dcf5f","type":"paragraph","text":"三月开日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ef216cabae"},{"id":"e2f99d152a","type":"paragraph","text":"第十七页上删去两句，因为不能或不愿加入那些人民团【体】的人们，例如资产阶级，富农，民主党派，民主人士，并不都是不良分子或落后分子","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ef216cabae"},{"id":"db09b36b96","type":"paragraph","text":"代表们讨论中或者有些好意见，可据以修改或充实这个报告。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ef216cabae"},{"id":"fc0fcf60c3","type":"paragraph","text":"又：三年准备十年建设的思想，请你在会议中讲一下，使他们","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ef216cabae"},{"id":"f899da0194","type":"subtitle","text":"有所准备。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ef216cabae"}],"page":{"id":"fa95c332af","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"ef216cabae","start":198,"end":199}}}},"__N_SSG":true}